OL,4,E`````````````````````````````R##^T#### 
OL,5,BBlock Party 2022.                      
OL,7,EThe Centre for Computing HistoryBare   
OL,8,Bkindly providing their classroom area  
OL,9,Bfor our semi-regular celebration of    
OL,10,Bteletext, videotext, and other blocky  
OL,11,Bdelights on theE23rdBandE24th of April.
OL,13,BThere will beEpanelsBandEworkshops,Bto 
OL,14,Bintroduce passing Bamboozle fans to the
OL,15,Bmore esoteric aspects of our hobby.    
OL,17,BThe museum will be open 10:00 to 17:00 
OL,18,Bon both days. SeeEschedule on p107.    
