OL,5,BThe Chunkytext service.                
OL,7,BChunkytext is run byE@ZXGuesserBwith   
OL,8,Bcontributions from the teletext and    
OL,9,BDigitiser communities.                 
OL,11,BIf there is anything you think should  
OL,12,Bbe on Chunkytext which isn't, or find  
OL,13,Bsomething which shouldn't be, drop us  
OL,14,Band email atEchunkytext@zxnet.co.uk    
OL,16,BIf you just want to talk teletext, you 
OL,17,Bcan find us on the Teletext Discord    
OL,18,BviaEdiscord.gg/JfytfS3xmg              
